"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/7/2170?source=see_link\">",
"      Congenital gonadotropin-releasing hormone deficiency (idiopathic hypogonadotropic hypogonadism)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <br/>",
"     The following organizations also provide reliable health information.",
"    </p>",
